sources.title: Missile to the Moon (1958) Lunar She-Devils Lure Earthmen to their Doom!
sources.description:
Matriarchal lunar society led by blind Queen Lido (K.T. Stevens) and traitorous Alpha (Nina Bara) hijacks Earth rocket pilot Steve (Richard Travis) and stowaway June (Cathy Downs) for survival plans. But convicts Gary (Tommy Cook) & Lon (Gary Clarke) ignite chaos‚Äîbattling rock creatures, a giant arachnid, and Alpha‚Äôs schemes to blast off alive!
